n discouraged from pursuing a career in these industries due to the inflexible working arrangements."},{"citations":{"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554":1.0},"text":"The UK Export Finance (UKEF) has also vowed to increase its support for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) that are led by women, and has set a target to increase its support for these businesses fivefold."},{"citations":{"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554":1.0},"text":"This is an important step towards creating a more diverse and inclusive business environment, and will help to create new opportunities for women in the maritime and construction industries."},{"citations":{"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554":1.0},"text":"In conclusion, the construction and maritime industries are undergoing a significant shift towards greater gender equality and diversity, with women taking on non-traditional roles and challenging traditional gender barriers."},{"citations":{"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554":1.0},"text":"This shift is being driven by a combination of factors, including the efforts of organizations such as the IMO, and the creation of new laws and policies that support flexible working arrangements and diversity and inclusion."},{"citations":{"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500":1.0},"text":"As a result, women are now able to excel in a wide range of roles in the construction and maritime industries, from crane operators to seafarers, and are helping to create a more diverse and inclusive business environment."},{"citations":{"485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500":1.0},"text":"The story of Farkhana Safargaleeva, a crane operator with 15 years of experience, is just one example of the many women who are succeeding in these industries, and is an inspiration to other women who may be considering a career in construction or maritime."},{"citations":{"f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_334447554":1.0},"text":"The future of th