{"is_ragtime":true,"metadata":{"team_id":"T146","run_id":"dog","topic_id":"1036","task":"multilingual","request_id":"1036","narrative_id":"1036"},"responses":[{"citations":{},"text":"Biohacking is a term used to describe the practice of using various methods and techniques to \"self-optimize\" and improve one's health and well-being, with the ultimate goal of prolonging one's life."},{"citations":{"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384":1.0},"text":"The concept of biohacking originated in Silicon Valley, where it is often associated with the use of technology and data to optimize physical and mental performance."},{"citations":{"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384":1.0},"text":"One of the key principles of biohacking is the idea of using nutrition and lifestyle changes to activate epigenetic modifications, which can help to awaken dormant genes and enhance the body's resources."},{"citations":{"73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384":0.5,"a76144f6-85cb-430b-92e8-d25a00492c0f_535307822":0.25},"text":"This can be achieved through various means, including calorie restriction, intermittent fasting, and the use of supplements such as metformin, resveratrol, and rapamycin."},{"citations":{"0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574":1.0},"text":"In addition to nutrition and supplements, biohacking enthusiasts also often use physical activity and exercise to improve their health and well-being."},{"citations":{"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925":1.0},"text":"This can include techniques such as cold-water therapy, which has been shown to have anti-inflammatory effects and improve mental clarity."},{"citations":{"7330daf3-723a-424d-a476-023fed1467cf_546361925":1.0},"text":"Other popular biohacking methods include the use of saunas, which can help to detoxify the body and improve cardiovascular health."},{"citations":{"0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574":1.0},"text":"Mental health practices, such as meditation and mindf