ism\" was chosen as the word of the year in 2018, highlighting the growing concern about the negative effects of tourism."},{"citations":{"a90fed0f-41a3-49e4-85e1-ade7b9b5f6fa_334539654":1.0},"text":"The Sedona International Film Festival has also addressed the issue of overtourism through a documentary series, featuring interviews with local residents and global experts."},{"citations":{"a90fed0f-41a3-49e4-85e1-ade7b9b5f6fa_334539654":1.0},"text":"Overall, the causes and consequences of overtourism are complex and far-reaching, requiring a comprehensive approach to mitigate its social, environmental, and economic impacts."}],"answer":[{"citations":{"a90fed0f-41a3-49e4-85e1-ade7b9b5f6fa_334539654":1.0},"text":"Overtourism has become a significant issue in various parts of the world, causing numerous problems for local residents and the environment."},{"citations":{"4bd649f2-da29-4279-8605-12dc0f8367d9_38011106":1.0},"text":"The influx of tourists to popular destinations such as Venice, Italy, has led to a decline in the quality of life for locals, with the number of daily tourists exceeding the local population of 50,000."},{"citations":{"4bd649f2-da29-4279-8605-12dc0f8367d9_38011106":1.0},"text":"This has resulted in overcrowding, higher prices, and a homogenization of shops, making it difficult for locals to afford basic necessities."},{"citations":{"5b952cf7-c179-453f-8644-d0cdcc3301f0_499344639":1.0},"text":"The environmental impact of overtourism is also a concern, with the World Travel and Tourism Council launching research on the climate footprint of the global travel and tourism industry."},{"citations":{"5b952cf7-c179-453f-8644-d0cdcc3301f0_499344639":1.0},"text":"The research covers 185 countries and will be updated annually to monitor the sector's impact on pollutants, energy sources, and water use."},{"citations":{"a90fed0f-41a3-49e4-85e1-ade7b9b5f6fa_334539654":1.0},"text":"In addition to environmental concerns, overtourism has also led to social issues