8d37-274568fbd581_918907066":1.0},"text":"The cost of non-traditional yoga classes can vary, but some studios offer classes for as low as $30 for an hour session, which includes a half hour class and a full hour of playtime with animals."},{"citations":{"abcc75c1-8606-43d7-9727-a5f0ef54e1bb_42404643":1.0},"text":"Overall, non-traditional yoga practices that fuse traditional movements with novel or entertaining elements are a great way to make yoga more accessible and enjoyable for a wider range of people, and can offer a unique set of benefits that can enhance overall health and well-being."},{"citations":{"abcc75c1-8606-43d7-9727-a5f0ef54e1bb_42404643":1.0},"text":"The rise of non-traditional yoga practices is expected to continue, with more studios and instructors offering classes that combine yoga with activities such as animal-assisted therapy or themed sessions, and they are perceived as a great way to make yoga more fun and engaging."},{"citations":{"f2191b5d-250b-4a7e-b4fb-3047f83a6829_974086854":1.0},"text":"In conclusion, non-traditional yoga practices are a great way to make yoga more accessible and enjoyable for a wider range of people, and can offer a unique set of benefits that can enhance overall health and well-being, and their popularity is expected to continue to grow in the coming years."},{"citations":{"7bc87769-b800-4b3c-8d37-274568fbd581_918907066":1.0},"text":"The benefits of non-traditional yoga practices, including animal-assisted yoga, are supported by research, which suggests that they can be a great way to improve physical fitness, reduce stress and anxiety, and enhance overall health and well-being."},{"citations":{"7c9126d4-1629-4a1a-aa4d-03a9c622b034_296262592":1.0},"text":"The perception of non-traditional yoga practices is that they are more fun and engaging, and can be a great way to make yoga more accessible and enjoyable for a wider range of people, but some people may view them as less effective or less traditional than more tradi